# Contribution & Community Guidelines

Thank you for your interest in contributing to the ASCII Hydra project!
Our goal is to create a cost-efficient, vendor-agnostic framework for creating Spark-based assets that run on local PySpark, Databricks, or AWS EMR.
We welcome contributions from developers, researchers, and community members who share our vision.
Please follow these guidelines to help maintain a clean, efficient, and collaborative project.

## How to Contribute